{"id":3,"date":"2025-05-02T18:33:33","date_gmt":"2025-05-02T18:33:33","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/box2041\/cgi\/addon_GT.cgi?s=GT::WP::Install::Cpanel+%28jdenmedi%29+-+127.0.0.1+%5Bnocaller%5D\/?page_id=3"},"modified":"2025-06-11T21:12:48","modified_gmt":"2025-06-11T21:12:48","slug":"privacy-policy","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/privacy-policy\/","title":{"rendered":"Privacy Policy"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><em>Effective Date: May 14, 2025<\/em><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">At Kuska Autism Services, your family\u2019s privacy, trust, and confidentiality are our top priorities. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information, including how we comply with the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. Information We Collect<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We may collect personal and health-related information that you voluntarily provide, including:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"\">Your name, phone number, email address, and city<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Information related to your child\u2019s autism diagnosis or care needs<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Insurance or provider details (if applicable)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Any information submitted through contact forms, phone calls, or emails<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We may also collect technical data (e.g., IP address, browser type) to improve our website functionality.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. HIPAA Compliance and Protected Health Information (PHI)<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">Certain information we collect may qualify as <strong>Protected Health Information (PHI)<\/strong> under HIPAA. PHI includes any health-related information that identifies you or your child and relates to diagnosis, treatment, or payment for healthcare services.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">Kuska Autism Services complies with all HIPAA regulations. We:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"\">Safeguard PHI using administrative, physical, and technical safeguards<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Limit access to PHI to authorized personnel only<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Require written authorization before using or disclosing PHI for purposes beyond treatment, payment, or healthcare operations (unless required by law)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. How We Use Your Information<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We use personal and health information solely to:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"\">Respond to inquiries and coordinate services<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Provide individualized support and care<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Contact you about appointments or service updates<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Fulfill legal or billing requirements<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We do <strong>not<\/strong> sell, rent, or share your information for commercial marketing purposes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Sharing and Disclosure of Information<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We may share information:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"\">With authorized team members or healthcare providers involved in your child\u2019s care<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">With insurance companies or billing entities (with appropriate safeguards)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">As required by law or in response to a legal request (e.g., court order or subpoena)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">All sharing is done in compliance with HIPAA and only on a need-to-know basis.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. Your Rights Under HIPAA<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">As a parent or legal guardian, you have the right to:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"\">Access and receive copies of your child\u2019s records<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Request corrections to inaccurate information<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Request restrictions on how we use or share PHI<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">Receive an accounting of disclosures<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li class=\"\">File a complaint if you believe your privacy rights have been violated<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">To make a HIPAA-related request, please contact us at <a href=\"tel:+18019807970\">801-980-7970<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>6. Security Measures<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We implement industry-standard practices and technologies to secure your data. These include encrypted communications, secure data storage, and access controls. Staff are trained on confidentiality and privacy best practices.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>7. Children\u2019s Privacy<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We only collect information about children with parental or guardian consent. All information is handled in accordance with both general privacy principles and HIPAA requirements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>8. Changes to This Policy<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">We may update this policy as our practices or legal obligations change. We encourage you to review it regularly. The updated version will include a new \u201cEffective Date\u201d at the top.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>9. Contact Us<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">For questions or concerns regarding this policy or your rights, please contact:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\"><strong>Kuska Autism Services<\/strong><br>95 E 2200 S, Bountiful, UT 84010<br><a href=\"tel:+18019807970\">801-980-7970<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"\">You may also file a complaint with the U.S. Department of Health &amp; Human Services. We will not retaliate against you for filing a complaint.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Effective Date: May 14, 2025 At Kuska Autism Services, your family\u2019s privacy, trust, and confidentiality are our top priorities. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information, including how we comply with the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA). 1. Information We Collect We may collect personal and health-related information [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","_et_pb_use_builder":"","_et_pb_old_content":"","_et_gb_content_width":"","footnotes":""},"difl_page_category":[],"class_list":["post-3","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":321,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3\/revisions\/321"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"difl_page_category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/difl_page_category?post=3"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}